comment_message_cleaned: This has been inspiring - former PM Brian Mulroney's and Minister Catherine McKenna's words reminded me of the role that small town's and rural communities played and continue to play in a sustainable future for our planet. As the mayor of the Town of Prescott in the 's and past and present participant in the movement toward a balanced and vigorous approach to sustainability it was an honour in the Canada C3 eedition. With my colleagues, I look forward to hearing Minister MacKenna's address at the Scaling Up conference on the bioeconomy in Ottawa next week and being further inspired!!

text_original_comment: This has been inspiring - former PM Brian Mulroney's and Minister Catherine McKenna's words reminded me  of the role that small town's and rural communities played and continue to play in a sustainable future for our planet.  As the mayor of the Town of Prescott in the 1980's and past and present participant in the movement toward a balanced and vigorous approach to sustainability it was an honour in the Canada C3 expedition.
